snippet.title: New Indie MMO - Teaser Cinematic
snippet.description:
Teaser Trailer for the Indie Online RPG, Order of the Elements.

Check out the development and support the Anti Pay-2-Win movement!

Discord - https://discord.com/invite/ZTb7juM
Patreon - https://patreon.com/orderoftheelements
Steam Page - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2617430/Order_of_the_Elements/?beta=0

Credit to the amazing Voice of Maria Gray for the female VO - https://www.mariagraymg.com/
